  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses the designation of a recreational trail as a state trail.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>establishes the process for designating a state trail;<hr><ltbullet>addresses management of state trails; and <hr><ltbullet>authorizes rulemaking by the Division of Outdoor Recreation to:<hr><ltbullet1>establish the process for completing and submitting an application; and<hr><ltbullet1>administer management of a state trail.",
